{"tid":2249523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解而家啲人咁鍾意批評文青？","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T11:45:28.000Z","uid":26833,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72cd82c5a7dcbb9720d2d0197d039c3d5d966aac","tid":2249523,"uid":26833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:31:38.000Z","msg":"例如話大南街 點點點 深水埗 點點點<br />\n多一個地方俾人休息 飲下咖啡 <br />\n又唔得？<br />\n<br />\n香港人已經好攰 旅行已經無得去<br />\n而家好似坐底飲杯咖啡 都係罪過咁<br />\n而啲人只識不停咁批評人<br />\n就算大南街唔開咖啡店 都只會係一個好多吉鋪嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n而家多個位俾人休息下 都要俾人話<br />\n<br />\n最諷刺係呢班批評文青嘅人 成日係大南街擺展<br />\n咁先好笑<br />\n<br />\n同埋呢香港唔係淨係得深水埗有露宿者 窮嘅人<br />\n<br />\n香港人好難滿足 <br />\n有時候 無論你做乜 都係錯架<br />\n所以咁多香港人有抑鬱自殺嘅念頭就係咁解<br />\n<br />\n有時候 批評少啲 香港會少啲人有抑鬱"},{"pid":"c436c0aca96ff83587dcbc7ff30a9e57e064db50","tid":2249523,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"因為嗰班唔係文青<br />\n係<span class=\"xx-large\">MK</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba49b1bcf01f49c409007adf4cef5c82eba33fc","tid":2249523,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:34:10.000Z","msg":"香港人不嬲鍾意批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n檢討自己把鬼 屌人先爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c274a8fd30f29ee8f49b998b8707f2399e5d90f4","tid":2249523,"uid":366655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫文青<br />\n坐喺咖啡店攞住杯咖啡po下ig又話自己文青<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">你MK嚟㗎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b40cd3b616264d4aa6332bff90f6b671b4d46cf4","tid":2249523,"uid":32442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"唔好理係跟風定真心鍾意<br />\n我覺得d香港indie band、本土電影、黑膠店、書店，媒體創作者因為咁而生存到都係好事<br />\n經典文學、政治書多左人討論 可能有d人會因為咁接觸而鍾意左呢"}]}